RailsCasts Episode #306: ElasticSearch Part 1

http://railscasts.com/episodes/306-elasticsearch-part-1

Commands used in episode

  brew install elasticsearch
  elasticsearch -f -D es.config=/usr/local/Cellar/elasticsearch/0.18.5/config/elasticsearch.yml
  rake db:setup

Require Ruby 1.9.2 or later to run example.
